Security and other important information
How long does Voodoo keep your data?
Personal data collected, received and processed for the purposes described in this policy is
not kept longer than necessary
by Voodoo.
Voodoo does not retain user level data for more thanÂ 13 months
except for the data collected for the purpose of its
